# Maintenance Strategy G

This project is a demo-focused UI prototype that shows how adaptive intelligence can support maintenance strategy generation.

The goal is not to build a full production website. The goal is to create a set of connected UI screens that demonstrate the concept, flow, and decision-making experience.

## Purpose

- Demonstrate how maintenance strategy inputs can be captured through UI
- Show how adaptive intelligence can shape recommendations
- Present linked screens that tell a clear concept story
- Support discussion, iteration, and stakeholder feedback

## Scope

This repository is for:

- UI concepts
- linked demo screens
- interaction flow ideas
- visual storytelling for the maintenance strategy process

This repository is not currently for:

- a complete production application
- full backend logic
- final deployment-ready code

## Working Approach

The UI sets in this project will be created progressively and guided through iteration. Each screen should help explain one part of the broader adaptive maintenance strategy workflow.

